title: Sample Book, Marburg Tapetan, 1954
description: Contains 37 samples of wallpaper with color alternatives. Includes embossed and varnished papers. Besides the Neue Wohnung collection of the Werkakademie, there is the Neue Form collection by Elsbeth Kupferoth, the Allegro collection (Erlesene Schopfungen) and the Opus collection.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Marburg Tapetan, 1954; Designed by Elsbeth Kupferoth (b. 1920); Germany; machine-printed; 26.5 x 25 x 1.5 cm (10 7/16 x 9 13/16 x 9/16 in.); 1954-152-1-1/39
